    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT343-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">tōḻi kiḻattiyai uṭaṉpōkku nayappak kūṟiyatu. </p>


        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Spoken by the confidante in order to persuade HER of
          going away together [with him]. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT343">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> niṉaiyāy vāḻi tōḻi naṉaikavu</l>
          <l> ḷaṇṇal yāṉai yaṇimukam pāynteṉa</l>
          <l> mikuvali yirumpulip pakuvā yēṟṟai</l>
          <l> veṇkōṭu cemmaṟuk koḷīi viṭarmukaik</l>
          <l> kōṭai yoṟṟiya karuṅkāl vēṅkai</l>
          <l> vāṭupūñ ciṉaiyiṟ kiṭakku</l>
          <l> muyarvarai nāṭaṉoṭu peyaru māṟē.</l>


        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Think, oh friend, of the way</l>
          <l rend="indent">[you] will move with the man from the land of high mountains,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">where the split-mouthed male of the very strong big tiger</l>
          <l rend="indent2">is resting, like a twig with fading flowers</l>
          <l rend="indent3">of the black-trunked Vēṅkai broken by the west wind,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">in a rock cave, after it had put red spots on the white tusks,</l>
          <l rend="indent4">because it sprung into the adorned face of a majestic</l>
          <l rend="indent8">elephant with wet temples .</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
